Archwizard Only Facilities
  
RMEDIT       Enter The Internal Room Editor
SHELL        All commands sent to TSS, until * typed
RAW <msg>    Raw Message Broadcast
SYSTAT       Running System Statistics (Defuncted under unix)
UPDATE       Exit Game and return to new version
TSS <cmd>    Execute shell command
INUM  <item> Returns games internal number for given object
DEBUGMODE    Enter debug information mode, gives obnums etc too
PATCH        Patch the running world file
PFLAGS	     Set players PFLAGS
 
Have Fun
  
           ---->(A)
